 show premiere on Disney Channel instead of Disney XD.}}\n |ProdCode        = 112\n |Viewers         = 1.09<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/showbuzzdailys-top-150-friday-cable-originals-network-finals-5-4-2018.html|title=SHOWBUZZDAILY's Top 150 Friday Cable Originals & Network Finals: 5.4.2018 \u2013 Showbuzz Daily|author=Mitch Metcalf|date=May 7, 2018|website=www.showbuzzdaily.com|accessdate=May 7, 2018}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary    = Scrooge and his family are stuck on the Island of Ithaquack, home of the [[Greek gods]], where Dewey and Webby try to search for ''The Spear of Selene'' and uncover the mystery of Della's disappearance. However, Dewey struggles with the possibility that his mother may not have been a good person. They later find out that ''The Spear of Selene'' does not belong to [[Selene]] ([[Nia Vardalos]]), goddess of the Moon, who reveals that Della was a great person and friend. Meanwhile, Donald is dragged into a competition to settle a dispute between Scrooge and [[Zeus]] ([[Michael Chiklis]]). [[Hercules|Storkules]] ([[Chris Diamantopoulos]]), Zeus' son and an acquaintance of Donald's, encourages him to continue adventuring, even in spite of Della's disappearance. \n |LineColor       = FFEF00\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 11\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 11\n |Title           = Beware the B.U.D.D.Y. System!\n |DirectedBy      = John Aoshima\n |WrittenBy       = {{StoryTeleplay|s=Francisco Angones, Madison Bateman, Colleen Evanson, Christian Magalhaes & Bob Snow|t=Angones}}\n |Aux2            = Benjamin Balistreri, Evon Freeman, Mark Garcia, Tanner Johnson & John Ramirez\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|5|11}}\n |ProdCode        = 114\n |Viewers         = 0.68<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/showbuzzdailys-top-150-friday-cable-originals-network-finals-5-11-2018.html|title=SHOWBUZZDAILY's Top 150 Friday Cable Originals & Network Finals: 5.11.2018&nbsp;\u2013 Showbuzz Daily|author=Mitch Metca