03547/2015/1|archive-date=2018-02-16|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|}\n\n=== [[Golden Raspberry Awards]] ===\n'''0 wins''' of 5 nominations\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:1em;\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:39em;\"| Nominated work\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:39em;\"| Category\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:5em;\"| Result\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2em;\" class=\"unsortable\"| {{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n| [[17th Golden Raspberry Awards|1997]]\n| ''[[She's the One (1996 film)|She's the One]]''\n| [[Golden Raspberry Award for Worst New Star|Worst New Star]]\n| {{Nominated}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"| [[31st Golden Raspberry Awards|2011]]\n| ''[[The Bounty Hunter (2010 film)|The Bounty Hunter]]''\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Golden Raspberry Award for Worst Actress|Worst Actress]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" {{Nominated}}\n| rowspan=\"3\"|\n|-\n| ''[[The Switch (2010 film)|The Switch]]''\n|-\n| ''[[The Bounty Hunter (2010 film)|The Bounty Hunter]]''\n| [[Golden Raspberry Award for Worst Screen Combo|Worst Screen Couple]] (<small>shared with [[Gerard Butler]]</small>)\n| {{Nominated}}\n|-\n| [[32nd Golden Raspberry Awards|2012]]\n| ''[[Just Go with It]]''\n| [[Golden Raspberry Award for Worst Screen Combo|Worst Screen Couple]] (<small>shared with [[Adam Sandler]]</small>)\n| {{Nominated}}\n|\n|-\n| [[36th Golden Raspberry Awards|2015]]\n| ''[[Cake (2014 film)|Cake]]''\n| [[The Razzie Redeemer Award|Razzie Redeemer Award]]\n| {{Nominated}}\n|\n|}\n\n=== [[Gracie Awards|Gracie Allen Awards]] ===\n'''1 win''' of 1 nomination\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:1em;\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:39em;\"| Nominated work\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:39em;\"| Category\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:5em;\"| Result\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2em;\" class=\"unsortable\"| {{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n|2012\n|''[[Five (2011 film)|Five]]''\n|[[Gracie Awards|Outstanding Drama]]\n|{{Won}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=ht